ms & Instructions ](/forms-instructions)\\n\\n    * [ Overview ](/forms-instructions)\\n\\n    * POPULAR FORMS & INSTRUCTIONS \\n    * [ Form 1040 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-1040)\\n    * Individual Income Tax Return \\n    * [ Form 1040 Instructions ](/instructions/i1040gi)\\n    * Instructions for Form 1040 \\n    * [ Form W-9 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-w-9)\\n    * Request for Taxpayer Identification Number (TIN) and Certification \\n    * [ Form 4506-T ](/forms-pubs/about-form-4506-t)\\n    * Request for Transcript of Tax Return \\n\\n    * [ Form W-4 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-w-4)\\n    * Employee\\'s Withholding Certificate \\n    * [ Form 941 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-941)\\n    * Employer\\'s Quarterly Federal Tax Return \\n    * [ Form W-2 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-w-2)\\n    * Wage and Tax Statement \\n    * [ Form 9465 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-9465)\\n    * Installment Agreement Request \\n\\n    * POPULAR FOR TAX PROS \\n    * [ Form 1040-X ](/forms-pubs/about-form-1040x)\\n    * Amended Individual Income Tax Return \\n    * [ Form 2848 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-2848)\\n    * Power of Attorney \\n    * [ Form W-7 ](/forms-pubs/about-form-w-7)\\n    * Apply for an ITIN \\n    * [ Circular 230 ](/tax-professionals/office-of-professional-responsibility-and-circular-230)\\n    * Regulations Governing Practice before the IRS \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n<::before><::after>\\n\\nSearch \\n\\nInclude Historical Content \\n\\n\\\\- Any -  No \\n\\nInclude Historical Content \\n\\n\\\\- Any -  No \\n\\nSearch \\n\\n##  Information Menu \\n\\n  * [ Help ](/help/let-us-help-you \"Help\")\\n  * [ News ](/newsroom \"News\")\\n  * [ Tax Pros ](/tax-professionals)\\n  * [ Sign in ](/your-account)\\n\\n\\n\\n##  File \\n\\n  * [ Overview ](/filing)\\n  * INFORMATION FOR\u2026 \\n  * [ Individuals ](/individual-tax-filing)\\n  * [ Business and self-employed ](/businesses)\\n  * [ Charities and nonprofits ](/charities-and-nonprofits)\\n  * [ International filers ](/individuals/international-ta